==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Choctaws
<hw>Choc"taws</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>; <sing><it>sing.</it>
<singw>Choctaw</singw>.</sing> <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld> <def>A tribe of
North American Indians (Southern Appalachian), in early times noted for
their pursuit of agriculture, and for living at peace with the white
settlers. They are now one of the civilized tribes of the Indian
Territory.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

